  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center mt-5 pb-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-5 d-flex flex-column mb-3 order-md-2">
      <h2 class="mb-4 display-5">
        <span class="d-block fw-800">Une sélection d'experts,</span>
        <span class="d-block fw-800">du contenu offert</span>
      </h2>
